Your Future’s So Bright... You Gotta Wear Shades 
Jumpstart your solar career.
View our Job Postings










 










When someone asks, “So, what do you do for a living?” wouldn’t it be cool to say, “Oh, I save the planet.” Okay, maybe it’s a little over the top, but at Sunrun, we’re changing the industry, making solar an affordable, money-saving option for our customers (and, yes, making Mother Earth a little cleaner too). We’re looking for the best and brightest to join our team of passionate, friendly people who have the desire to be part of something big. Be a part of something that matters, without sacrificing fun!
Empower yourself with the sun
With a solar career at Sunrun, be part of a company that’s the biggest, best and most respected, while working in an atmosphere that encourages you to develop, grow, make friends and be yourself. Check out our solar job openings to find the perfect match.
 
