Creating a Platform for Change
Solar engineering careers at Sunrun. 
View all job postings










 










At Sunrun, we’re creating a technology platform for the solar industry that boosts efficiency, quality and affordability. Our solar platform lets us rapidly get your ideas into users’ hands, going from inception to production in days. We want people who are driving for results… who are unafraid of occasional failure. And we don’t pair program continuously; we pair when it’s most helpful. At Sunrun, you’ll work on projects that really matter. Projects that help meet the world’s critical challenges. You’ll also be part of an amazing group of friendly, passionate people who thrive in a fast-moving, rapidly evolving and adaptable environment.
Empower yourself with the sun
Sunrun careers offer you an opportunity to develop, grow, have fun, and be yourself. The vibe is open and informal, and the folks are friendly. Sunrun has open solar engineering jobs in Java Architecture, Java Engineering, Front-end JavaScript Engineering, QA and more. We need passionate people, just like you, who want to be part of the future of energy. 

            

More on Sunrun Engineering
Wondering what it's like to work in the Engineering Department at Sunrun? What kinds of people make up our team? How we're changing the solar industry?
Download our presentation

 






