Sunrun Solar States














 










Arizona


With the most sun out of any state, it's no wonder home solar power in Arizona is so hot right now. Take advantage of its most powerful natural resource.








California


Our BrightBox home solar storage system can help Californians maximize their solar savings. And with one of the highest utility rates in the country, there's no better time to save big on solar.








Colorado


300 days of sunshine a year means plenty of Colorado solar power to go around. Power towards a clean energy future in a state that puts the environment first and start saving today.








Connecticut


Connecticut has the highest utility rate in New England.1 That's why set it's setting its sights on solar power. Help it reach its renewable energy goals while you lock in low and predictable rates for 20 years.








Delaware


The country's First State could also be the first in solar power. Now's your chance to cash in on Delaware's solar-friendly credits--there's never been a better time to go solar.








Florida


The Sunshine State is packed with solar potential. And when you're also cranking up the AC, a home solar system seems like a pretty bright idea to start saving. But where to start? We're here to help.








Hawaii


With the highest energy costs in the U.S., locals are all too familiar with unpredictable utility bills. Start harnessing the power of Hawaii's most brilliant natural resource and enjoy solar power 24/7 with BrightBox Hawaii.








maryland


Maryland is on the fast track to solar. Its solar capacity grew over 109% in the past year, and it's just getting started.2 Get on board and see how you could gain energy independence the Free State.








massachusetts


The state that ranks high in smarts also has one of the highest energy rates in the country.3 As a Massachusetts homeowner, you could be saving big on a long solar-powered future with low, predictable rates and more.








nevada


Nevada ranks in the top 5 for solar capacity, and it shouldn't stop there. As one of the sunniest states in the country, Nevada is full of solar potential that's just waiting to be turned into clean and affordable energy.








New Hampshire


It may have one of the most stunning landscapes in New England, but New Hampshire's energy rates are some of the highest in the country. Do the Blue Mountains some good while saving big on your electricity bill.








New Jersey


We've saved New Jersey homeowners over $18 million dollars so far, and we're just getting started. Take advantage of this solar-friendly state's numerous incentives and credits while they're still available.








New Mexico


280 days of sun means there's plenty of rays to go around. Sunrun has the answer to saving big on your electricity bill so you can take advantage of all that New Mexico living has to offer.








New York


New York is full of solar potential. As one of the top 10 solar markets in the country, its government is committed to making the state a solar powerhouse. Be the savvy New Yorker that you are and see how much you could save.








oregon


Preserving natural resources is a mission any Oregon homeowner can stand behind. Combine that with the added bonus of a lower electric bill and Oregonians have one powerful money and planet-saving duo.








pennsylvania


Pennsylvania is booming, and so is its solar power. The state wants its homeowners to go solar, and does its part by offering generous tax incentives and credits. Ready to start saving?







Rhode Island


Rhode Island has the highest electricity rates in the country,9 but with the help of Sunrun, we make solar easy while helping you save big on your electricity bill.







South Carolina


With new legislation making it easier than ever for South Carolinians to take advantage of federal and state tax rebates, and electric rates rising all across the state, solar has never been a better bet in the Palmetto State.








Texas


Want to beat the heat while taking control of your electric bill? Here at Sunrun, we can help homeowners in the Lone Star State gain energy independence while maximizing solar savings with Think Energy.








utah


Our simple solar packages will help you save on your electricity bill while protecting the beauty of the Beehive state. Lock down predictable rates energy rates and go back to enjoying what you love most about living in Utah.








vermont


Vermont may not be the largest state, but when it comes to solar, it's leading the pack with a renewable energy goal of 90% by 20507. We can help Vermont reach this goal while helping you save big on your energy bill.8







washington dc


Initiatives like Clean Energy D.C. are already working towards making the nation's capital a greener place to live by 2032.5 We're here to help it reach its goal while saving you money on your electricity bill.








Wisconsin


The Badger State has some of the highest electricity rates in the region.6 Thankfully, we're here to make going solar in simple in Wisconsin so you can get back to what actually matters (like cheering on the Packers).








