Power Up Your Life 
Choose a Sunrun career. 
View all Job Postings










 










We may not wear flowers in our hair—but we’re part of something big. 
Something that matters. And it’s happening at a company that’s the most respected in the solar industry. Sunrun careers offer you an opportunity to develop, grow, have fun, and be yourself. Here, you can help reinvent the future of energy, while working in a diverse atmosphere where the vibe is open and informal, and the folks are friendly and approachable. We need passionate people, just like you, to fill Sunrun jobs in sales, marketing, construction and engineering, just to name a few.
Our values: 
 
            

#1 Be inventive.
To stay on top of the game, we have to be constantly ready to reinvent the game.

 
            

#2 Be customer obsessed.
We treat customers like we would want to be treated ourselves. Really, ridiculously well.

 
            

#3 Be real.
Talk to each other - lots. Great ideas rarely happen in a vacuum.


            

#4 Be adaptable.
We may not always know exactly what's next, but we know we'll be ready for it.








