GET STARTED FOR AS LITTLE AS $0 DOWN




BrightSave Monthly:

Start saving with $0 down today.



Sunrun's BrightSave™ Monthly makes going solar and saving on your electric bill about as easy as it gets. You can get started for little to $0 down and you just pay a low, locked-in rate for the solar power the system produces over your 20-year agreement. With BrightSave Monthly, you only pay for the solar power, not the solar panels, which helps you save 20% on your electricity bill.* Not only that, Sunrun takes complete care of the system. We guarantee solar system performance and if the system doesn’t produce the electricity we promised—for any reason you’ll receive a refund for the difference.**








ENJOY TOTAL PEACE OF MIND AND MAXIMIZE SAVINGS




BrightSave Prepaid

Electricity costs keep rising, but with Sunrun's BrightSave™ Prepaid, you purchase all your solar power upfront, locking in 20 years of electricity at today’s prices. You buy the power not the panels, so because Sunrun owns your system, we take care of all the tax filing and paperwork. Even better, the upfront payment with BrightSave™ Prepaid can be less than owning your system outright. You get the benefit of owning your power without the hassle of maintenance or repairs. Sunrun takes complete care of the system. We guarantee solar system performance and if the system doesn’t produce the electricity we promised, you’ll receive a refund for the difference.**








PURCHASE A CUSTOMIZED SYSTEM FROM SUNRUN TODAY




BrightBuy

With Sunrun’s BrightBuy™, you purchase the entire solar system upfront, so you own your system and your savings. You just pay a one time upfront cost to Sunrun for the hardware and installation then you gain complete ownership of the system. That means no monthly payments or having to worry about rising energy costs, hidden fees, and surprise hikes on your electric bill. So whenever your power company raises their rates on your neighbors, you can pat yourself on the back for making the smart choice to go solar with Sunrun.








FINANCE YOUR SYSTEM AND START SAVING ON DAY 1




BrightAdvantage

Own your system with Sunrun’s hassle-free financing with BrightAdvantage™. This means fast approvals, low fixed interest rates, no upfront payment and no penalties associated with traditional solar loans—all while taking advantage of available solar tax credits and rebates. Loan options facilitated by Sunrun are unsecured (does not require you to use your house as collateral), free of any penalties or hidden provisions, and provide multiple term options at very competitive borrowing costs, giving you the freedom to go solar on your terms.







 
