BrightSave Monthly
GET STARTED FOR AS LITTLE AS $0 DOWN
Learn More



              Go solar with BrightSave Monthly and start saving today. For as little as $0 down, you can go solar and save on your monthly electricity costs. Sunrun offers complete peace of mind with free monitoring, maintenance, repairs, and insurance for 20 years. We offer a best-in-class performance guarantee*, and free overproduction. Lock in a low monthly payment to protect against rising utility prices and take control of your electricity bill. Read More >

Learn More




BrightSave PrePaid
ENJOY TOTAL PEACE OF MIND AND MAXIMIZE SAVINGS
Learn More



              Go solar with BrightSave Prepaid and lock in the best value product that Sunrun has to offer. Skip the hassle of ownership and let Sunrun deliver 20 years of electricity, worry-free. Sunrun offers complete peace of mind with free monitoring, maintenance, repairs, and insurance for 20 years. We offer a best-in-class performance guarantee*, and free overproduction.
 Read More >

Learn More




BrightAdvantage
Finance your system and save on day one
Learn More



With BrightAdvatnage,  you’ll own your system and your savings from Day one. We offer fast approvals, low fixed interest rates, no upfront payment, and no pre-payment penalties. You’ll also be able to take advantage of all available solar tax credits, rebates, and incentives. Sunrun offers a best-in-class workmanship warranty, and we only work with dependable equipment providers that offer solid warranties. Read More >

Learn More




BrightBuy
PURCHASE A CUSTOMIZED SYSTEM FROM SUNRUN TODAY
Learn More



              With BrightBuy, you’ll own your system and your savings. Sunrun will design and install a system customized to fit your needs. When you pay for the equipment and installation upfront, you get to enjoy clean and reliable energy without worrying about rising energy costs, hidden fees, and surprise hikes on your electric bill. You’ll also be able to take advantage of all available solar tax credits, rebates, and incentives. Sunrun offers a best-in-class workmanship warranty, and we only work with dependable equipment providers that offer solid warranties. Read More >

Learn More




BrightBox
ENJOY TOTAL HOME ENERGY CONTROL TODAY
Learn More



              BrightBox combines Sunrun’s solar power generation with a smart battery solution to provide energy control and savings. Enjoy safe, clean, and reliable backup power to keep your family powering forward in the event of a blackout. BrightBox saves you money by seamlessly optimizing when a home uses electricity generated from solar, stored in the battery, or from the grid. Purchase or lease BrightBox from Sunrun today! Read More >

Learn More




















