San Jose, CA is perfect for home solar savings
Get a Free Quote



 










Home solar in San Jose, California
From the Children's Discovery Museum to the San Jose Municipal Rose Garden to simply hanging out around town, San Jose is a gem of the greater Bay Area. Which is probably why you love living here.
As a homeowner, you benefit from being pretty close to the SF metro and an uncanny amount of sunshine all year. With all that on your plate, it's about time you check out home solar and stack up some savings of a lifetime.
That's because rising energy rates in California are squeezing homeowners like you for more and more money every year. Utility companies rely on unpredictable energy markets, which is why the costs always get passed on to you.
With all that pressure on your wallet, we're sure you're looking for new and better ways to power your home. That's why it's time you consider switching to home solar. With home solar panels from Sunrun, you can save 20%* on your electric bill over the lifetime of the system.
And that's just the beginning. With Sunrun, you can enjoy the type of support you need to power your home worry-free all year.
Going solar in San Jose is affordable & easy
As the largest dedicated home solar company in the country, we know a thing or two about the sun, just like you. In fact, we think that our love for savings is what helps set us apart.
Pair it with our expert knowledge, our simple processes, and professional partnerships, and you've got a really passionate team ready to show you just how great solar in San Jose can be. You don't have to believe us either.
Just talk to one of our solar consultants and learn more about the perks of going solar with Sunrun, including:
Saving 20%* on your electric bill.
Multiple, flexible options for financing.
A custom-designed home solar system.
Protection from rate increases for the lifetime of your system.
Solar installation by trusted and certified Sunrun partners.
The best warranties in the industry.
24/7 live monitoring of your home solar system.
With all these great benefits choosing Sunrun couldn't be easier. So what're you waiting for? 1-408-310-4613 or sign up for a free quote today and get a headstart on cleaner energy and better savings in no time.
Tom & Glorianne's San Jose, CA Solar Story
Tom and Glorianne wanted to reduce their energy costs and fight global warming by getting . After considering proposals from several traditional PV installation companies which required them to purchase panels and perform their own maintenance, they heard about Sunrun.
Tom and Glorianne chose Sunrun because it gave them the lowest overall cost, in addition to the peace of mind that comes with Sunrun's maintenance and repair, and monitoring services.
Like many people, they were used to writing big monthly checks to their power company in San Jose. With their electricity rate rising steadily every year, it is no wonder they wanted to get a home solar system.
Because Sunrun offers a low fixed rate for home solar electricity that's less than their utility rate, Tom and Glorianne were able to reduce their monthly energy costs and easily budget for electricity over the long term.
Tom and Glorianne got proposals from several other companies for home solar in San Jose. Sunrun was able to save them over 50% of the upfront cost to make their San Jose home solar, and offer unbeatable long-term savings as well. For Tom and Gloriane, the long-term economic benefits of Sunrun's power purchase agreement (PPA) was undeniable. It was easy to see that Sunrun was the best deal available for solar in San Jose.
Since Sunrun guarantees the electricity generation from their system, Sunrun is on the hook to monitor and maintain the system at no additional cost. Because Sunrun only gets paid for performance, Tom and Glorianne are confident knowing that Sunrun will be watching their San Jose solar system like a hawk to make sure it delivers all the electricity Sunrun promises. Or they'll get money back.
 








